{% from "govuk/components/inset-text/macro.njk" import govukInsetText %}

<div>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Find out what funding you can get from the Sustainable Farming Incentive (SFI) to help you manage your land more sustainably and improve food production.
  </p>

  <p class="govuk-body">You can use this service to:</p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>
      filter and print actions you may want to apply for
    </li>
    <li>
      hide actions that are not relevant to you 
    </li>
    <li>
      access guidance on how to apply for funding for each action
    </li>
  </ul>

  {% set eligibleText %}
    <span>This service does not confirm you're eligible to apply for SFI.  <a class="govuk-link" target="_blank" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/what-to-do-before-you-apply-for-an-sfi-agreement">Read the SFI guidance to check if you're eligible and how you can apply.</a></span>
  {% endset %}


  {{ govukInsetText({
    html: eligibleText
  }) }}

  <p class="govuk-body">
    The summaries of each SFI action in this service are not part of the terms and conditions for any SFI agreement you have with DEFRA or the Rural Payments Agency (RPA). They do not change your existing agreement in any way. The summaries are not the actions that clause 1.5 of the SFI 2023 terms and conditions refers to.
  </p>  
  
  <p class="govuk-body">
    The following list of SFI actions signposts you to the full guidance on how to apply for each action.
  </p>
</div>